				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You need to reset the VRAM address after you're done writing to memory. To do this, write once to $2000 (to select which nametable to start rendering at) and then write twice to $2005 (to specify the horizontal and vertical scroll).</div>

					
